Usage:
  looper daemon [flags]

Subcommands:
  install  Install the managed daemon binary
  status   Show daemon status
  start    Start the daemon
  stop     Stop the daemon
  restart  Restart the daemon
  logs     Show daemon logs

Flags:
  --force                     Overwrite existing installed daemon binary
  --full                      Show all retained daemon log lines, including rotated log files
  --lines <count>             Line count
  --startup                   Show daemon startup logs instead of main logs

Global Flags:
  --config <path>             Config path (`~/.looper/config.toml` by default; also supports .yaml, .yml, and .json)
  --daemon-mode <mode>        Daemon mode
  --daemon-restart-policy <policy> Daemon supervisor restart policy: never, on-failure, or always
  --daemon-restart-throttle-seconds <seconds> Daemon supervisor restart throttle
  --db-path <path>            Database path
  --fixer-agent-timeout-seconds <seconds> Fixer agent execution timeout
  --gh-path <path>            GitHub CLI path
  --git-path <path>           Git binary path
  --host <host>               Server host
  --instructions-enabled <bool> Enable custom instructions
  --json                      Emit JSON output
  --log-dir <path>            Daemon log directory
  --looper-path <path>        Looper CLI path
  --osascript-path <path>     osascript binary path
  --package-auto-upgrade-enabled <bool> Enable automatic upgrade checks for this command
  --planner-agent-timeout-seconds <seconds> Planner agent execution timeout
  --port <port>               Server port
  --reviewer-agent-timeout-seconds <seconds> Reviewer agent execution timeout
  --roles-fixer-triggers-author-filter <filter> Fixer author filter: current-user or any
  --roles-reviewer-behavior-loop-enabled-by-default <bool> Enable reviewer follow-up loops by default
  --roles-reviewer-behavior-loop-max-iterations-per-head <count> Deprecated; ignored by reviewer loop filtering
  --roles-reviewer-behavior-loop-max-iterations-per-pr <count> Deprecated; ignored by reviewer loop filtering
  --roles-reviewer-behavior-loop-min-publish-interval-seconds <seconds> Reviewer loop minimum publish interval
  --roles-reviewer-behavior-loop-quiet-period-seconds <seconds> Reviewer loop quiet period
  --roles-reviewer-behavior-review-events-blocking <event> Reviewer event for blocking findings: COMMENT or REQUEST_CHANGES
  --roles-reviewer-behavior-review-events-clean <event> Reviewer event for clean runs: COMMENT or APPROVE
  --roles-reviewer-discovery-triggers-enable-self-review <bool> Allow reviewer triggers to process self-authored pull requests
  --worker-agent-timeout-seconds <seconds> Worker agent execution timeout

Examples:
$ looper daemon install
$ looper daemon start
$ looper daemon stop
$ looper daemon restart
$ looper daemon status
$ looper daemon logs --lines 50
$ looper daemon logs --full
